description:
This is a 11 minute workout called '10 MINUTE FULL BODY STRETCH ROUTINE' from the channel BullyJuice.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: LET'S GET LOOSE , increase recovery quality, and prevent future injuries with this 10 minute movement routine! Mobility is extremely important. We beat our bodies up and it's so easy to forget to tend to them after we're done with working out. The difference between you being good and great are the little things like warming up and cooling down!
